Feat:
SANDWICH MUNCHER

During a short rest, you take a few minutes to make yourself a delicious snack in the form of a sandwich, sliced diagonally into two perfectly-proportioned sandwich wedges. As a bonus action, you may take a sandwich wedge and either eat it, or feed it to an ally or friendly creature within 5 feet of you that is capable of eating it. Consuming a sandwich wedge heals 1d4 HP and grants advantage to Constitution checks and saving throws for 1 minute.
